OL,5, Heather Lawrence was shocked at the    
OL,6, state she found her 90-year-old mother,
OL,7, Violet, in when she visited her in     
OL,8, hospital.                              
OL,10,F"The bed was soaked in urine. The      
OL,11,Fcontinence pad between her legs was    
OL,12,Falso soaked in urine, the door wide    
OL,13,Fopen, no underwear on. It was a mixed  
OL,14,Fward as well," Heather says.           
OL,16,F"I mean there were other people in     
OL,17,Fthere that could have been walking up  
OL,18,Fand down seeing her, with the door wide
OL,19,Fopen as well. My mum, she was a very   
OL,20,Fproud woman, she wouldn't have been    
OL,21,Fwanted to be seen like that at all."   
